  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Biology (Agric &amp; Envir Sc)              : A phylogenetic-based overview of the tree of life and examination of relationships between major taxa, from bacteria and archaea to eukaryotes. Evolution will be discussed via topics including: evolution by natural selection, neo-Darwinism and alternatives, myths and misconceptions in evolution, species and speciation.

          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
